title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Jul 2 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Jul 2 2022
description:
Blood on Biden's hands: 50 illegals dead in San Antonio tractor-trailer tragedy. Latest on Uvalde police response. Buck says, "Biden is not a leader. He may be president, but he's not a leader." Hillary Clinton trashes Clarence Thomas. Clay says, " Thomas' getting attacked on a different level, has been for much of his career, because message needs to be sent from Democrats, 'You can't be black and be conservative.'" Republican candidate for governor, Andrew Giuliani, joins Clay and Buck to make his pitch on primary day in New York.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
